TopicTitle: A problem whit ksp 1.11.1.3066 whit mods.

Articles.Content:
I installed some mods and launched KSP. When it launched Module Manager had a fatal error. I seed log and deleted the errors that were linked whit mods. (This happend multiple times.) I reinstalled Module manager and launched KSP. It launched but then Tweak Scale had a fatal error and said that my savegames can be corupted. Can someone help me how to fix this?
